sourcesContent:
let main = {
  width: "calc(100vw - 10px)", 
  height: "calc(100vh - 6px)",
  overflowY: "hidden",
  overflowX: "hidden"
}

let containerMiddle = {
  display: "flex",
  height: "92%"
}

let loadingContainer = {
  position: "absolute",
  width: "160px",
  height: "30px",
  left: "45%",
  top: "50%",
  borderRadius: "5px",
  backgroundColor: "#07405b",
  color: "white",
  lineHeight: "20px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "10px",
  cursor: "default"
}

let loadingBar = {
  width: "1px",
  marginLeft: "10px",
  backgroundColor: "#e4f7ff",
  height: "20px"
}

export {
  main,
  containerMiddle,
  loadingContainer,
  loadingBar
}
